        <h2>Our Process</h2>
        <p>We follow a streamlined process to ensure quality service and customer satisfaction:</p>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Consultation:</strong> We begin with a site visit to assess your power needs and recommend the best inverter solution.</li>
            <li><strong>Design:</strong> We provide a customized design tailored to your specific requirements, including the size and placement of the inverter system.</li>
            <li><strong>Installation:</strong> Our certified technicians handle the installation, ensuring everything is set up according to industry standards.</li>
            <li><strong>Testing:</strong> We test the system to ensure proper operation and energy efficiency.</li>
            <li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> We offer ongoing support and maintenance to keep your inverter system running smoothly.</li>
        </ol>
